The package boost-concept-check is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS concept_check)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::concept_check)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_concept_check REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::concept_check)
